{"title":"牧马英雄","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧马英雄〔好来宝〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出席全国少数民族群众"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"业余艺术观摩演出会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古代表团演唱组　集体创作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拿四胡调好了弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱一唱公社的牧马员；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠心耿耿的老那顺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄事迹到处传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬尽初春天气寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云遮住了半边天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风搅雪花上下翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫草原遭风险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪怒吼耍威风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风扑面难睁眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风刺肌骨如针扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层困难摆眼前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若马群顺风跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群马可能会分散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东一群来西一群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦失散太危险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧马老手那顺呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心如大河急浪滚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身跨上快骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗖的一声向前奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气跑到山坡上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方仔细瞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心爱的马群无踪影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想必顺风跑远了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱的是蒙族一老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人那顺英雄胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪漫天马群飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层雪幕望不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顺心急似油煎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身跨马一溜烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要有俺那顺在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕马群飞上天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细看群马踏雪迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象趟雪顺风跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如若不去紧追赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"势必马群更难保。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕山高沟深路坷坎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵马飞越快如箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕积雪三尺三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬鞭趟雪驰向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"策马跳涧又翻山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观察地形跟踪追赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺风惊跑的散马群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于出现在前边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人那顺把风向辨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"测知马群奔北边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵马越过万重险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中挥动套马杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朔风怒啸盖满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顺心红斗志坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕大雪与风寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨不回马群誓不还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪纷纷下得玄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马群照旧驰向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉擦眼仔细看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐马撒缰追上前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左右抡起套马杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭拨马群往回返。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风雪中夺马群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风餐露宿两昼夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保住马群忘了累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴高采烈往回转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎面又来了一群马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破雪海一溜烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东一片，西一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疾蹦乱跳冲向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽不认识这群马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体财产当心肝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身是胆的老那顺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心把马往回拦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一匹一匹忙归拢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一五一十把数点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动手中的套马杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两群散马并成团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦住马群向南返，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一群散马奔北边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨回散马并成团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的马群脱了险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顺搏斗了两昼夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺马英雄美名传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手持的套马杆迎风摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着马群往回返，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄满面带笑容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢欢喜喜回家转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顺是个好社员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤胆忠心为集体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍己为公护马群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家向他来学习。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}